snippet.title: PS1 Kero Kero King Gameplay
snippet.description: Showing off some of the gameplay. I just got this game in the mail the night before this upload so I'm just starting to figure things out a bit. The gameplay is a bit different from the PS2/Gamecube sequel Ribbit King.
